{"tid":1742318,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"法律撚閪解答 - 陪審團，口供， 聲援，上庭","createTime":"2019-11-20T17:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T13:56:05.000Z","uid":138442,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f5ac6f34d9ff54de7e90d05115556d5d07517b2","tid":1742318,"uid":138442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:45:16.000Z","msg":"希望幫到大家！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>陪審團 ：</strong><br />\n首先就近日報章提及的陪審員資訊更正一下。<br />\n<br />\n根據法例規定，任何21至65歲香港居民，只要精神健全而無任何失明、失聰或其他無行為能力、品格良好及對採用語言（中文或英文）熟悉，均有資格出任陪審員。<br />\n<br />\n於香港既大學畢業，正常應會收到確認信件。如於外國就讀大學，或未收到確認信，可自行向人事登記處遞交申請，只須於書件列明希望加入陪審團名單，並附上指定文件即可。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>登記成為陪審員須知</ins><br />\n<br />\n寄送地址： <br />\n香港灣仔告士打道7號入境事務大樓12<br />\n樓 行政主任（人事登記）支援<br />\n<br />\n所需文件： 學歷證明副本，已填妥之ROP 18表格<br />\n<br />\n信內所需資料： 申請人中英文姓名，香港身份證號碼，聯絡電話，簽名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遞交ROP 18表格只係更新資料，唔會影響被抽中嘅機率。所以外國大學畢業無影響， 都係一樣己有陪審團資格，只係睇抽唔抽中入pool。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院司法常務官每兩年編製一份陪審員臨時名單，該名單於十月或以前擬定，然後在翌年二月或以前確認。<br />\n<br />\n區院無係陪審團，高等法院先有。但暴動罪係嚴重刑事罪行，有機會係高院審。檢控官決定單案件去區域法院或者高等法官。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>口供 ：</strong><br />\n好多群組已經講過被拉要講咩野，唔多講。真係落完身分證資料，問你咩都話&quot;我無野要講&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>聲援 ：</strong><br />\n相信大家唔想手足覺得自己係condom，但區院坐位好有限，真心留比親友會好啲。太多人聲援係會影響官既心情同感受。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>上庭：</strong><br />\n衣著記住整齊斯文呢啲唔多提，但記住眼神！眼神誠懇！"},{"pid":"eb4a81d3c544d49ea386940e1c96f2aa3627480f","tid":1742318,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:49:24.000Z","msg":"高院好似都未必有陪審團？<br />\n其實用唔用陪審團的準則係點？"},{"pid":"85834e8294db6cee8791509cce4136450cca0970","tid":1742318,"uid":51860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:52:21.000Z","msg":"實用po<br />\n推"},{"pid":"bfaacddc517f43da654a537a0f9bdb74b85e3321","tid":1742318,"uid":23392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb4a81d3c544d49ea386940e1c96f2aa3627480f","tid":1742318,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:49:24.000Z","msg":"高院好似都未必有陪審團？<br />\n其實用唔用陪審團的準則係點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"區域冇 高院(CFI, CA)都有<br />\n上左高院(CFI)就有"},{"pid":"6a9a2ad691e86c5d692fa0c693e55db0527e2106","tid":1742318,"uid":138442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"上面篇野dup左成晚，沖涼休息先<br />\n大家可以留低問題，聽日有時間盡覆！"},{"pid":"a0d097fcebafcb2aafc07232c05db0db4f4521e8","tid":1742318,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a9a2ad691e86c5d692fa0c693e55db0527e2106","tid":1742318,"uid":138442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"上面篇野dup左成晚，沖涼休息先<br />\n大家可以留低問題，聽日有時間盡覆！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:56:03.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"a4afd59dc04ec43fd423c6979a45345190f43156","tid":1742318,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfaacddc517f43da654a537a0f9bdb74b85e3321","tid":1742318,"uid":23392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb4a81d3c544d49ea386940e1c96f2aa3627480f","tid":1742318,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:49:24.000Z","msg":"高院好似都未必有陪審團？<br />\n其實用唔用陪審團的準則係點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"區域冇 高院(CFI, CA)都有<br />\n上左高院(CFI)就有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:59:15.000Z","msg":"Sorry 講清楚 高院=原訟庭CFI同CA上訴法庭<br />\n而原訟庭係有Jury嘅"},{"pid":"2622dbaff6efbd36880b9f8f3b9c29167a3b4bd0","tid":1742318,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a8e32707aab5e79aca60dc38880ea56efab1cf","tid":1742318,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2622dbaff6efbd36880b9f8f3b9c29167a3b4bd0","tid":1742318,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d8954e89d2d64a34dbfbce8c6aba7cc8526fd7","tid":1742318,"uid":305242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:21:01.000Z","msg":"推唔到但想推！！！<br />\n各位巴絲幫手推啊啊啊啊啊啊！！！"},{"pid":"30effbe90424a8dc3b4b1dc36f089686bf2784ae","tid":1742318,"uid":104797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"請問asso仔有冇資格做陪審團？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13046bdecbdfcc9c1c2c0cdba9b36ff6d2d0f490","tid":1742318,"uid":63786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"Top up degree又得唔得呢?"},{"pid":"69213206bdd0ec4a40d241b7365b1844c6333477","tid":1742318,"uid":188480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:57:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b19afca96564d42cb2fc35bf09d85cf9f59aa720","tid":1742318,"uid":298767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30effbe90424a8dc3b4b1dc36f089686bf2784ae","tid":1742318,"uid":104797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"請問asso仔有冇資格做陪審團？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:58:43.000Z","msg":"有呀"},{"pid":"14c9198afdf2fe34aefd39c68e561b8ad6d8ac67","tid":1742318,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:02:07.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"d7ce5af7313607577ef6b22c15c4144568e42e5c","tid":1742318,"uid":157671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13046bdecbdfcc9c1c2c0cdba9b36ff6d2d0f490","tid":1742318,"uid":63786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"Top up degree又得唔得呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:10:36.000Z","msg":"得啊"},{"pid":"680b760c6efa0714020e991edba5b46a8ae491bb","tid":1742318,"uid":287649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2622dbaff6efbd36880b9f8f3b9c29167a3b4bd0","tid":1742318,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:16:33.000Z","msg":"程序上陪審員係唔需要響庭上解釋判罪嘅原因。責任只係睇晒所有呈堂證供之後決定。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做過"},{"pid":"cadfcd1ece74e45d6192e3fce576536fab5a39af","tid":1742318,"uid":287649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:20:17.000Z","msg":"即使收到信話你嗰日抽中左，嗰日仲要過三關。<br />\n<br />\n第一關係要前一晚上網睇之後嗰日需唔需要陪審員。<br />\n第二關就係嗰日上到庭要抽籤。<br />\n第三關就係雙方律師無反對之下宣誓後正式成為陪審員。"},{"pid":"10e03ebf565ab73f9976001c173353a5317e1f40","tid":1742318,"uid":104797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13046bdecbdfcc9c1c2c0cdba9b36ff6d2d0f490","tid":1742318,"uid":63786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"Top up degree又得唔得呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"asso得top up degree更加得"},{"pid":"b471bb88a562959c6ca320ac2c855f5658f56bdc","tid":1742318,"uid":138442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2622dbaff6efbd36880b9f8f3b9c29167a3b4bd0","tid":1742318,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"我搵返陪審團條例比大家望望<br />\n<br />\n宣布裁決的方式<br />\n陪審團的裁決，在任何情況下須由首席陪審員於公開法庭及在該陪審團全體成員在場時宣布；如屬刑事訴訟程序，則宣布時被控人亦必須在場，裁決並須即時由司法常務官或法庭書記主任記錄；司法常務官或法庭書記主任在記錄裁決前，須詢問陪審團在裁決上是否一致，或贊成裁決多數的比例，以及裁定原告或被告勝訴，如屬對刑事案件被控人的裁決，則須詢問陪審團裁定被控人罪名成立或不成立。陪審團須宣告原告或被告勝訴的一般裁決，或宣告罪名成立或不成立的一般裁決，或就案件的事實作出特別裁決︰<br />\n但陪審團可就針對被控人的部分指控而裁定該人無罪，並裁定該人其餘的罪名成立。<br />\n(由1911年第51號修訂；由1911年第63號附表修訂；由1934年第23號第3條修訂；由1999年第26號第3條修訂)<br />\n<br />\n27.陪審團在裁決上意見不一致<br />\n凡陪審團在任何案件中退席及受隔離以便考慮其裁決，而在同一次開庭期之中審訊的所有其他案件審結之前仍未作出裁決，或法庭充分地覺得該陪審團在裁決上無法意見一致，且不能達致上述的多數裁決，則法庭可解散該陪審團，並安排另選任新陪審團，着其宣誓及委以任何被控人所涉及的案件，而該訴訟、訟案、告發或公訴須猶如從未選任最初的陪審團一樣，進行審訊。<br />\n(由1911年第51號修訂；由1911年第63號附表修訂；由1929年第8號第6條修訂)"},{"pid":"d40f48e4302c84ae5f5bae024a20f606c412b007","tid":1742318,"uid":313062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:35:16.000Z","msg":"品格良好 &lt;-點衡量?"},{"pid":"654df06cc5ac715f80fd14e53deef928d25b58a4","tid":1742318,"uid":138442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30effbe90424a8dc3b4b1dc36f089686bf2784ae","tid":1742318,"uid":104797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"請問asso仔有冇資格做陪審團？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"當然有, 基本係大專or以上就已經有, 不過登記遞張ROP 18更新資料無壞真係."},{"pid":"68450b9a7aaea3b2bbc0c5acd4ce1862e42de0cd","tid":1742318,"uid":138442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7ce5af7313607577ef6b22c15c4144568e42e5c","tid":1742318,"uid":157671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13046bdecbdfcc9c1c2c0cdba9b36ff6d2d0f490","tid":1742318,"uid":63786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"Top up degree又得唔得呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:10:36.000Z","msg":"得啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"Ching幫手答左, 不過講多次, 有心做update下自己資料無壞"},{"pid":"139e19f3489dad6496b4cf6c685fdd4f3dd2b95e","tid":1742318,"uid":156679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"有用post 留個名先"},{"pid":"e562638d55c21940cafc32ce3a28139bae62302f","tid":1742318,"uid":138442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cadfcd1ece74e45d6192e3fce576536fab5a39af","tid":1742318,"uid":287649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:20:17.000Z","msg":"即使收到信話你嗰日抽中左，嗰日仲要過三關。<br />\n<br />\n第一關係要前一晚上網睇之後嗰日需唔需要陪審員。<br />\n第二關就係嗰日上到庭要抽籤。<br />\n第三關就係雙方律師無反對之下宣誓後正式成為陪審員。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"Thanks Ching.  <br />\n真心大家要留意返唔係收到信唔得於你就係陪審員, 唔好誤會。<br />\n高院每宗有陪審團參與的審訊都係公開法庭抽籤, 再係被傳召出席既陪審員中選出。但係刑事案控辯雙方律師有權反對某D人出任陪審員，法庭亦可以即時批准豁免某些人士出任陪審員，所以被傳召出席的陪審員人數通常多過實際需要。<br />\n<br />\n如果第一輪抽籤未被選中的人士，可能要係當天/其他日期去其他法庭參加另一個陪審團的抽選。"}]}